<br />

<br />
The mem blur try was a nice though. Unfortunatly, GE isnt a zone with wide area so unless both memblur stick at the same time it wouldnt have worked.. But maybe they were far enough of each other (kind of doubt it with what you describe) What you should have done is mez one then mez the other one down the hall. then go in middle of them and invis (according none see invis). That way you still have all your option on whichever will be memblurred.
<br />

<br />
Another option would have been to mez them both and try to run out of chase aggro (dunno how far it is in GE so might be impossible 8/ )
