				<td colspan="2"><span>Mez resists can be a hassle, but with only two mobs it is no big deal. Just debuff the mob with Occlusion of Sound (level 55 I think) or Harmony of Sound (level 65) with a drum equipped and then mez. You should be able to keep two mobs mezzed until the cows come home if you do this (debuff mob1, mez mob 1, debuff mob2, mez mob2.....rinse and repeat).
<br />

